{"tid":1306481,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】重飲緊鉛水on99的啟晴邨巴絲入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-11T07:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:24:43.000Z","uid":204163,"like":175,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"616e9de5f03cfe66fe84bcfe8e0a29915a49b1fd","tid":1306481,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"已經忍夠呢條邨<br />\n鉛水<br />\n鎗擊案<br />\n周浩鼎條廢柴靠我地入立法會<br />\n到底呢條邨重要犯幾多錯<br />\n<br />\n我要改變<br />\n雖然條邨好多蝗<br />\n但都好多細路<br />\n佢地就係未來<br />\n<br />\n區議會就到<br />\n有無人想收梁婉婷條八婆皮？<br />\n我唔係咩政治勁的人<br />\n但我想參選<br />\n係自不量力<br />\n定放手一搏？<br />\n<br />\n我希望，呢條邨唔係真係咁垃圾<br />\n所以，我希望住係呢度的巴絲可以出一份力<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲都想選，我十分願意做你的助選團<br />\n<br />\n現在未有定案<br />\n所以，需要你的討論<br />\n同行動"},{"pid":"b69c2cd5f27db06e99db275cdf07e4ab81b1b8da","tid":1306481,"uid":146975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8b1da25ae71b90b11e8ca8049e61613042b1d7f","tid":1306481,"uid":204163,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"有野想講，歡迎暢所欲言<br />\n就算唔係啟晴邨巴絲，都可以講下<br />\n始終我政治素人，咩都唔識，要靠大家指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd1ff524e24623b54e4e7134e1fd9d5c7f18de2","tid":1306481,"uid":224298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630b37da7eff3f6b51c3534d5a6e6cefa79e3642","tid":1306481,"uid":259907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f24ceed0ceb0cc9ebfdff32dc2676115a5565789","tid":1306481,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4492